{"id": "TLCOE-2010001", "structData": {"test_id": "T-ON-00001", "confluence_page_id": "TLCOE-2010001", "title": "[ON WEB] Sticky add-to-bag button on PDP scroll - Jun 2022", "brand": "Old Navy", "brand_code": "ON", "market": "US", "value_stream": "PDP", "channel": "Web", "channel_section": "Mobile Web", "device": "Mobile", "audience": "Loyalty Members", "tactic": "Time Savings", "primary_kpi": "OPV Conversion Rate", "secondary_kpis": ["PDP Certona Engagement Rate", "PDP Views Per Visit", "Visits Split (Visit/Visitor)", "Variation Overlap", "Search Engagement Rate", "Free Shipping Threshold Crossings"], "vendor": "Optimizely (Client-Side)", "test_type": "Client-Side", "start_date": "2022-06-13", "end_date": "2022-10-11", "duration_days": 120, "sample_size_per_arm": 15000000, "mde_pct": 0.44, "confidence_pct": 80, "power_pct": 80, "exposure_pct": 100, "split": "50/50", "outcome": "Flat", "primary_kpi_delta_pct": -0.11, "net_rpv_delta_pct": 0.19, "aos_delta_pct": 0.2, "visits_total": 30000000, "incremental_revenue_usd": 0, "averted_loss_usd": 0, "recommendation_text": "No change. Keep the control as the production experience.", "recommendation_adopted": "N/A", "learning_snippet": "FLAT: 'Sticky PDP ATB' on Old Navy PDP (Mobile Web) did not move OPV Conversion Rate beyond MDE (0.44%). No change. Keep the control as the production experience.", "related_test_ids": [], "hypothesis": "If we apply 'Sticky PDP ATB' on Old Navy PDP (Mobile Web) to loyalty members, then we expect a lift of at least 0.44% on OPV Conversion Rate because a sticky atb on mobile pdp keeps the primary cta visible during long scrolls.", "problem_statement": "On Old Navy PDP, the current control experience does not sufficiently support opv conversion rate for the loyalty members segment. Based on prior time savings-tactic learnings across the discount tier, we want to evaluate whether the proposed change moves the needle within the 120-day window.", "short_label": "Sticky PDP ATB", "confluence_url": "https://gap.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/TLCOE/pages/TLCOE-2010001", "sha256_source": "62b0a613bcac05385ddec9deaec90fe59208508f651b3f2563cf35cd7615c367"}, "content": {"mimeType": "text/html", "uri": "gs://gap-genai-discovery-corpus-md/pages/TLCOE-2010001.html"}}
{"id": "TLCOE-2010002", "structData": {"test_id": "T-GAPF-00002", "confluence_page_id": "TLCOE-2010002", "title": "[GAPF WEB] Loyalty point earn estimator on PDP - Mar 2026", "brand": "Gap Factory", "brand_code": "GAPF", "market": "US", "value_stream": "PDP", "channel": "Web", "channel_section": "Mobile Web", "device": "Mobile", "audience": "Returning Visitors", "tactic": "Value", "primary_kpi": "Add-to-Bag Rate", "secondary_kpis": ["Free Shipping Threshold Crossings", "PDP Certona Engagement Rate", "Promo Code Application Rate", "Variation Overlap", "Bag Edit Rate"], "vendor": "Rokt", "test_type": "Client-Side", "start_date": "2026-03-14", "end_date": "2026-05-13", "duration_days": 60, "sample_size_per_arm": 15000000, "mde_pct": 0.43, "confidence_pct": 80, "power_pct": 80, "exposure_pct": 10, "split": "90/10 (holdback)", "outcome": "Loss", "primary_kpi_delta_pct": -0.56, "net_rpv_delta_pct": -0.37, "aos_delta_pct": -0.95, "visits_total": 30000000, "incremental_revenue_usd": 0, "averted_loss_usd": 1702154, "recommendation_text": "Do NOT roll out. Re-test only after redesign of the failing module.", "recommendation_adopted": "No (averted loss)", "learning_snippet": "LOSS: 'PDP points estimator' on Gap Factory PDP (Mobile Web) moved Add-to-Bag Rate by -0.56% (Net RPV -0.37%); averted ~$1,702,154 in revenue loss. Do NOT roll out. Re-test only after redesign of the failing module.", "related_test_ids": [], "hypothesis": "If we apply 'PDP points estimator' on Gap Factory PDP (Mobile Web) to returning visitors, then we expect a lift of at least 0.43% on Add-to-Bag Rate because showing 'you'll earn x points' on pdp reinforces loyalty value and lifts conversion among members.", "problem_statement": "On Gap Factory PDP, the current control experience does not sufficiently support add-to-bag rate for the returning visitors segment. Based on prior value-tactic learnings across the discount tier, we want to evaluate whether the proposed change moves the needle within the 60-day window.", "short_label": "PDP points estimator", "confluence_url": "https://gap.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/TLCOE/pages/TLCOE-2010002", "sha256_source": "74cf58aafb5e085189a58efa1498245cd09708ba92edf7014c6ce1ebae03029a"}, "content": {"mimeType": "text/html", "uri": "gs://gap-genai-discovery-corpus-md/pages/TLCOE-2010002.html"}}
